\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces Training convergence per curriculum stage (8 stages with $\geq 50$ logged episodes shown; short interrupted stages omitted). Each line is one stage, coloured light-to-dark with stage index. \textbf  {Left:} mean episode reward --- early stages (4--6) converge at large negative values; later stages (7, 10, 13, 15, 16) converge to $3$--$5\times 10^6$. \textbf  {Right:} TD loss --- all stages show the spike-then-converge profile. Raw values in transparent colour; EMA ($w=0.9$) in bold.}}{63}{figure.caption.27}\protected@file@percent }
